Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know... I'm not really sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but he came asking about {\i1}uminaoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how he heard about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I came all this way with nothing to show for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Islanders are tough people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that glow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bright to be sea-fireflies and\N too dim to be fishing lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... you can see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know a lot about things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes... It's how I make my living.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa's back. Let's have dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the man from this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome to come over if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There are too many snakes around to camp out at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, we have company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's a rarity...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he, Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's Isana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So she is. Sorry, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it'll appear anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,since the moon is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come here to ask about {\i1}uminaoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That glow always appears around that rock over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a trench we call the Dragon's\N Palace below that rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,People who lose their lives there are reborn looking exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Isana look like a normal child to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the {\i1}uminaoshi{\i0} of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio... no one has ever survived this disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't be able to come back unless we submerge her while she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me... Mio...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of dying and going away forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to fall asleep thinking that I will come back here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, tomorrow is the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The full moon is finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... don't you want to see your mother again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I do, and so do all our relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all waiting for Mana to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's been hard on you to lose your husband and then your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All the more reason having a child will give you something to live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, please... You're the only one we can turn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If seeing that child will comfort you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,then I will give birth to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But the child is no longer my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me that you won't call her Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Any one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If a person swallows it, it will become a child who will look the same
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,as the person we submerged \Nin the sea within the past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That was how Isana was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Any chance she's the child of your late husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband died two years before Isana was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what that child is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but she did appear human...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no denying that you gave birth to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better if you just think of her as a child that looks a lot like her grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mio...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When that happens, this is what Mommy does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I imagine myself as a huge fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}swimming slowly downward into the quiet, blue ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then before I know it, I'm asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Isana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They say I'm Grandma's {\i1}uminaoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that child is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When she was about six, she was bitten by a snake and almost died, but she was reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman over there is one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon after she got married, a shark attacked her and she was reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Her husband waited nearly twenty \Nyears to marry her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all reborn and are living happy lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel at a loss when someone calls me "Mana,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't bother me since Mom \Ndoesn't call me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm happy to have been born to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this ocean, this island, everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be unsafe to approach the glow at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll wait for them to spawn at full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll stay until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow look at how lovely that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,An island where one can regain lost loved ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,An island where one can choose never to say goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In that sense, this is a true paradise...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A child that resembled my mom... I was able to feel that way when she was a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I don't know what \Nmy mother looked like as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But as she got bigger, \Nher face changes little by little...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything, such as her \Npersonality and minute habits,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is becoming close to that of the mother I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But she looks just like her and calls me Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The daughter I gave birth to and\Nraised doesn't seem like my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming from deep down in the Dragon Palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those globules... I think they're created by some sort of mushi, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any proof, but it all makes sense if you think of it this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What I found inside those globules \Nwas the embryos of various animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The form fundamental to all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that one who swallows a globule
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes pregnant with a child identical to the one who was submerged at sea
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,suggests that this mushi can return animals to their very embryos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That child is physically identical to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, she'll resemble her more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But since she was born and raised by you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,she cannot turn into your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To her, you are every bit her "mother".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I have to be strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of leaving tomorrow \Nif the weather will allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't know what to do if I stay here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right to take away your happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ginko...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mom is about to die, I'm going to give birth to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine life without Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'd better wait and see today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be a typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The storm's getting worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know there are actually\Ntimes when you can't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. It's just that I know a good way to fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When you can't sleep, it helps if you imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're a huge fish swimming down into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Swim past the coral, with \Nthe remora or such at your side...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly downward into the dark deep...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll gradually...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I'm a little... thirsty...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Wait here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be... strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to get swept out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My boat is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Isana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go near that glow! It'll eat you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rush in! We'll approach cautiously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're surrounding the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Isana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Isana, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darn... I can't... fight this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they eat me like this, will they\Nturn me into an embryo as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a time before everything begins...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gosh... that's a really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}... joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're letting go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Get out of the water quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The storm has... passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And... why did they suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The moon is out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I know only a very little about these mushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,they seem to glow to attract and capture animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,then return them to their essence\N before discharging them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That is probably their nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be able to say they're mushi that feed on the "time an animal lived".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you both know about those mushi very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it time and your issues will work themselves out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, Isana,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you jumped into the water without\Na second thought, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared the lights out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they ate your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you would've seen her again if you gave birth to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But then they would've eaten up \Nthe time Mom had lived, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather see Mom die while she's still my mom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,than give away her entire lifetime to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You think just like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what I'd expect of my child...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On that island, uminaoshi will probably continue as a regular occurrence,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}helping to put the dying at ease
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and filling the void in the hearts of those left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps being able to die without having that wish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,3820)\i1}is a rare and fortunate blessing.
